title: December Debuts: To be Not Reading... or not to be Not Reading?
description:
"Not Reading Debuts" ( <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading+Debuts" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading+Debuts</a>  ) are part of the <a href=" http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://thepiratebay.se/tag/Not+Reading</a>  project, and contain all first issues published and/or released during a given month that made an uploader's personal cut.

The month being December 2014 and the uploader being me in this case, obviously.




Cover:     <a href=" http://gesserit.000space.com/meta/yuq/users/29/766/gIvnW0BjGx.png" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://gesserit.000space.com/meta/yuq/users/29/766/gIvnW0BjGx.png</a>




Contains:   Eternal             #1 (of 4) - Boom Studios - Crime / Dystopian / Sci-Fi

            Rumble              #1        - Image        - Fantasy / Mystery / Noir

            Squarriors          #1 (of 4) - Devil's Due  - Drama / Dystopian / War

            They're Not Like Us #1        - Image        - Crime / Drama / Superhero


            Four titles this time - about half from Image, as usual; one from Boom
            Studios; and one from Devil's Due, which we've not seen here before. :)
